---
description: Personal website — Astro static portfolio conventions
globs: src/**/*.astro,src/**/*.ts,src/**/*.css,astro.config.mjs
---

- Read `docs/PROJECT_BRIEF.md` and `docs/ARCHITECTURE.md` before large changes; follow `docs/TASKS.md` for current priorities.
- Stack: Astro 6 + TypeScript (strict) + Tailwind 4. Prefer static patterns; avoid adding a server/API for MVP scope.
- Match existing layout and tone: professional, clear spacing, accessible landmarks and focus styles where interactive.
- No `any`; no secrets in source. New dependencies need a short note in `docs/DECISIONS.md`.
- Do not change MVP scope without updating `docs/PROJECT_BRIEF.md`.
